cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method for incremental learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The method involves regularization and sampling techniques, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
